constructor.details: Uses clone factory pattern to save space

params._factory: Factory used to get info of JoePairs
params._penaltyCollector: Address that collects all withdrawal penalties
params._router: Router used to create LP on Trader Joe AMM

params._floorPrice: Price of each token in AVAX, scaled to 1e18
params._issuer: Address of the project issuing tokens for auction
params._issuerTimelock: Amount of time issuer's LP will be locked for during phase 3
params._maxAllocation: Maximum number of AVAX each participant can commit
params._maxWithdrawPenalty: Maximum withdrawal penalty that can be met during phase 1
params._phaseOneStartTime: Timestamp of when launch event will start
params._token: Token that will be issued through this launch event
params._tokenAmount: Amount of tokens that will be issued
params._tokenIncentivesPercent: Additional tokens that will be given as incentive for locking up LPs during phase 3 expressed as a percentage of the issuing tokens for sale, scaled to 1e18
params._userTimelock: Amount of time users' LPs will be locked for during phase 3

returns._0: The number of launch events ever created

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setRJoePerAvax(uint256).details: Configured by team between launch events to control inflation

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

numLaunchEvents().notice: Returns the number of launch events

setPenaltyCollector(address).notice: Set address to collect withdrawal penalties

setPhaseDuration(uint256,uint256).notice: Set duration of each of the three phases

setPhaseOneNoFeeDuration(uint256).notice: Set the no fee duration of phase 1

setRJoePerAvax(uint256).notice: Set amount of rJOE required to deposit 1 AVAX into launch event

userdoc.notice: Factory that creates Rocket Joe events
